item.title: CVE-2019-4086|2024-08-04T19:26:27.917Z -- ibm -- cloud%20application%20performance%20management
item.description: IBM Cloud Application Performance Management 8.1.4 could allow a remote attacker to hijack the clicking action of the victim. By persuading a victim to visit a malicious Web site, a remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability to hijack the victim's click actions and possibly launch further attacks against the victim. IBM X-Force ID: 157509.
